		      		<h3>Welcome to Cibar </h3>
		      		<p class="sep_hoz">Cibar incorporated is a software development company located in Colorado Springs, Colorado. 
			      		Founded in 1969, Cibar has a broad range of experience in developing software applications for 
			      		international banking customers, including Letters of Credit, Collections, Foreign Loans, 
			      		Wholesale Demand Deposit Accounting, Cash Letters, Wire Transfers, Imaging, OFAC checking, 
			      		and Banker's Acceptances. 
