					 <h3>Why Cibar?</h3>
      <ul class="sep_hoz">
        <li><b>Stability:</b></li>
        <li>Cibar has been in business for over 46 years and has been in the Trade Finance Industry since 1973.<br></li>
        <li><b>Focus:</b></li>
        <li>For the past 38 years, Cibar's entire focus is on our Trade Finance Applications.</li>
        <li><b>Knowledge:</b></li>
        <li>Cibar's average employee tenure is 15 years.</li>
        <li><b>Security:</b></li>
        <li>Cibar provides the bank with a copy of the source code.</li>
        <li><b>Compilance:</b></li>
        <li>Cibar offers interfaces to multiple OFAC systems as part of GTSnet.</li>
        <li><b>Latest and Greatest:</b></li>
